Adds the v2 monorepo plumbing without touching v1 entrypoints.

* pnpm-workspace.yaml: include apps/* + packages/* alongside legacy
  artifacts/* lib/* lib/integrations/* scripts infra entries.
* turbo.json: pipelines for typecheck, build, test, lint, dev, clean.
* tsconfig.base.json: add path aliases for @gv/ui, @gv/api-client,
  @gv/types, @gv/config + dom libs + esModuleInterop + resolveJsonModule.
* Makefile: bootstrap, up, down, typecheck, test, migrate, seed,
  verify, openapi, codegen, dev, build, clean targets.
* package.json: rename to godsview@2.0.0-rc.0, add turbo dev dep,
  add v2 dev/build/typecheck/test scripts that scope to @gv/* and
  leave v1 verify:* scripts untouched.
* README.md: top banner pointing at docs/blueprint and quickstart.
* .gitignore: .turbo, .next, dist, .pytest_cache, .mypy_cache,
  .ruff_cache, .venv, *.egg-info, cdk.out, openapi codegen staging.

